1
00:01:29,580 --> 00:01:33,130
[Cage of Shadows]

2
00:01:33,700 --> 00:01:36,190
[Episode 19]

3
00:01:40,920 --> 00:01:44,450
"On the screen, the candle's shadow
deepens as night grows old.

4
00:01:45,360 --> 00:01:48,160
The Silver River slants
and the morning stars grow cold."

5
00:01:48,160 --> 00:01:50,840
Perhaps it just depicts a scene like this.

6
00:01:53,330 --> 00:01:54,620
You are...

7
00:01:54,640 --> 00:01:55,840
Liu Yuan?

8
00:01:59,580 --> 00:02:00,890
Exactly.

9
00:02:01,730 --> 00:02:03,170
Yang, let's go.

10
00:02:06,120 --> 00:02:07,380
Please stay, Miss Lin.

11
00:02:07,600 --> 00:02:09,000
I have no ill intentions.

12
00:02:09,979 --> 00:02:11,410
However, after spending several days here,

13
00:02:11,410 --> 00:02:12,980
I've been overcome by boredom.

14
00:02:12,980 --> 00:02:15,060
All I want is a mere chat with someone.

15
00:02:19,430 --> 00:02:21,000
What beautiful scenery today.

16
00:02:21,000 --> 00:02:22,160
It is truly rare.

17
00:02:22,480 --> 00:02:23,170
Miss Lin,

18
00:02:23,240 --> 00:02:24,440
if you are in the mood,

19
00:02:24,460 --> 00:02:25,790
why not stay here with me

20
00:02:25,890 --> 00:02:26,800
to taste some tea

21
00:02:26,800 --> 00:02:27,930
and admire the moon?

22
00:02:29,370 --> 00:02:30,530
[Auspice from the East]

23
00:02:37,190 --> 00:02:38,030
Prefect Wang,

24
00:02:38,200 --> 00:02:41,220
what brings you to my place
in the middle of the night?

25
00:02:41,240 --> 00:02:42,640
I had to rush here at night

26
00:02:42,640 --> 00:02:43,770
for a serious matter

27
00:02:43,790 --> 00:02:45,050
that can't be delayed.

28
00:02:45,240 --> 00:02:49,040
What exactly is this highly confidential
and urgent matter?

29
00:02:49,160 --> 00:02:50,680
Prime Minister, do you know about

30
00:02:50,680 --> 00:02:51,800
Lingya Tower?

31
00:02:52,640 --> 00:02:53,720
What tower?

32
00:02:55,050 --> 00:02:56,240
Lingya Tower.

33
00:02:59,550 --> 00:03:01,190
Lingya Tower...

34
00:03:02,960 --> 00:03:04,140
What's this place for?

35
00:03:04,140 --> 00:03:05,370
Rumor has it that it was set up

36
00:03:05,370 --> 00:03:07,020
by powerful figures in secret.

37
00:03:07,020 --> 00:03:09,870
To have fun, they make death row inmates
fight for their lives in there.

38
00:03:09,870 --> 00:03:12,740
Many officials in the court
are deeply involved.

39
00:03:13,160 --> 00:03:14,280
In the long run,

40
00:03:14,400 --> 00:03:16,400
I'm afraid this will harm the state.

41
00:03:17,120 --> 00:03:17,920
Oh?

42
00:03:19,310 --> 00:03:20,550
I can't believe

43
00:03:21,040 --> 00:03:24,100
such acts of defiance would occur
under my governance.

44
00:03:25,579 --> 00:03:27,760
This is the list of related officials

45
00:03:27,780 --> 00:03:29,700
that I've managed to gather.

46
00:03:30,100 --> 00:03:32,230
It is for your review, Prime Minister.

47
00:03:41,390 --> 00:03:43,610
How audacious of these people!

48
00:03:44,070 --> 00:03:47,200
This matter involves
numerous officials at all levels,

49
00:03:47,410 --> 00:03:48,530
even including...

50
00:03:51,310 --> 00:03:52,560
Including who?

51
00:03:53,350 --> 00:03:55,079
You are actually a nice person.

52
00:03:55,480 --> 00:03:56,520
It's a real pity

53
00:03:56,880 --> 00:03:58,940
that my heart belongs to someone else

54
00:03:59,160 --> 00:04:00,620
and has no room for another man.

55
00:04:00,620 --> 00:04:01,680
It doesn't matter.

56
00:04:02,090 --> 00:04:04,670
I'm already content with
a simple chat with you

57
00:04:04,670 --> 00:04:06,070
like a confidant of yours

58
00:04:06,120 --> 00:04:06,980
under the moon.

59
00:04:09,360 --> 00:04:10,260
Word has it

60
00:04:10,640 --> 00:04:12,720
that you deliberately cut your own face

61
00:04:12,720 --> 00:04:14,850
to avoid being married to another man.

62
00:04:16,410 --> 00:04:19,140
I suppose you also find me ridiculous,
don't you?

63
00:04:20,170 --> 00:04:21,250
No, I really don't.

64
00:04:21,519 --> 00:04:23,950
Instead, I find you deeply admirable

65
00:04:24,040 --> 00:04:25,320
for taking that action.

66
00:04:25,320 --> 00:04:26,840
Prior to entering this mansion,

67
00:04:26,840 --> 00:04:27,840
I kept wondering

68
00:04:28,320 --> 00:04:30,890
what kind of woman

69
00:04:30,910 --> 00:04:32,640
would have the courage to do so.

70
00:04:32,640 --> 00:04:34,500
I'm afraid my face under this veil

71
00:04:34,520 --> 00:04:35,680
might frighten you.

72
00:04:36,130 --> 00:04:38,190
I consider it a blessing of a lifetime

73
00:04:39,520 --> 00:04:41,510
to see your face, Miss Lin.

74
00:04:42,320 --> 00:04:43,780
Why would I be frightened?

75
00:05:01,150 --> 00:05:02,150
What do you think?

76
00:05:03,950 --> 00:05:05,430
The sight of your face

77
00:05:06,160 --> 00:05:06,920
reminds me

78
00:05:07,400 --> 00:05:08,800
of a line of poetry—

79
00:05:09,080 --> 00:05:11,410
"Scars steel her jade-like soul of grace.

80
00:05:11,860 --> 00:05:14,260
Her smile outshines the spring in bloom."

81
00:05:15,080 --> 00:05:16,940
Nian'an spoke highly of you to me.

82
00:05:17,360 --> 00:05:19,840
No wonder you could pass the imperial exam
with him in the same year.

83
00:05:19,840 --> 00:05:21,570
You are indeed knowledgeable.

84
00:05:24,240 --> 00:05:26,760
Prime Minister, the new son-in-law
of your choice, Liu Yuan,

85
00:05:26,760 --> 00:05:27,840
is also involved.

86
00:05:28,490 --> 00:05:31,970
[Editor of the Imperial Academy, Liu Yuan]

87
00:05:29,400 --> 00:05:32,000
Liu Yuan is a frequent visitor
to Lingya Tower.

88
00:05:32,080 --> 00:05:35,540
He has also committed several acts
of corruption and bribery.

89
00:05:36,560 --> 00:05:39,720
Worrying that you might be
deceived by him,

90
00:05:39,980 --> 00:05:41,710
I specially came to inform you.

91
00:05:42,000 --> 00:05:45,440
I didn't expect Liu Yuan
to be this kind of person.

92
00:05:50,090 --> 00:05:51,020
Prefect Wang,

93
00:05:51,720 --> 00:05:53,060
you did a great job.

94
00:05:54,590 --> 00:05:57,860
Only with pillars of the state like you

95
00:05:58,030 --> 00:06:00,290
can the imperial court prosper forever.

96
00:06:00,760 --> 00:06:02,560
I'm honored by your high regard,
Prime Minister.

97
00:06:02,560 --> 00:06:05,600
I was just fulfilling my duty.

98
00:06:06,400 --> 00:06:08,680
This matter is too importance

99
00:06:08,700 --> 00:06:10,220
to be taken lightly.

100
00:06:10,980 --> 00:06:12,650
I wonder who else is engaged in this

101
00:06:12,650 --> 00:06:14,730
besides you.

102
00:06:15,850 --> 00:06:17,270
Rest assured, Prime Minister.

103
00:06:17,270 --> 00:06:19,590
I haven't told anyone else yet.

104
00:06:19,620 --> 00:06:20,580
I even came

105
00:06:20,600 --> 00:06:22,010
to your residence alone.

106
00:06:22,440 --> 00:06:24,500
This visit is only known to you and me.

107
00:06:26,720 --> 00:06:28,000
Very good.

108
00:06:28,640 --> 00:06:30,080
Excellent.

109
00:06:49,880 --> 00:06:50,940
It's getting late.

110
00:06:51,610 --> 00:06:52,810
I shall take my leave.

111
00:07:00,560 --> 00:07:01,810
My Lady.

112
00:07:01,840 --> 00:07:03,320
My Lady!

113
00:07:07,320 --> 00:07:08,200
My Lady,

114
00:07:08,220 --> 00:07:09,190
are you alright?

115
00:07:13,400 --> 00:07:15,130
I'll bring Miss Lin to her room.

116
00:07:15,160 --> 00:07:17,560
As for you, go get some rest.

117
00:07:26,220 --> 00:07:28,820
If you weren't
the Prime Minister's daughter,

118
00:07:28,940 --> 00:07:31,070
who would have such patience with you?

119
00:07:33,370 --> 00:07:34,690
After we share

120
00:07:34,950 --> 00:07:36,590
a bed tonight,

121
00:07:38,500 --> 00:07:40,860
let's see if you can still be so arrogant

122
00:07:40,909 --> 00:07:42,570
and self-conceited.

123
00:08:02,600 --> 00:08:03,600
It's you?

124
00:08:04,440 --> 00:08:05,770
What are you doing here?

125
00:08:09,880 --> 00:08:10,920
Just now, that punk

126
00:08:10,920 --> 00:08:12,820
slipped drugs into your tea and pastries,

127
00:08:12,820 --> 00:08:14,550
seeking a chance to defile you.

128
00:08:14,960 --> 00:08:16,760
If I hadn't caught him in the act,

129
00:08:17,220 --> 00:08:18,560
I'm afraid you wouldn't even

130
00:08:18,560 --> 00:08:20,690
know how your life was ruined tonight.

131
00:08:20,960 --> 00:08:22,240
What an outrage!

132
00:08:22,860 --> 00:08:24,610
I thought he was a decent gentleman,

133
00:08:24,610 --> 00:08:26,940
but he is actually an animal
in human form!

134
00:08:30,520 --> 00:08:31,480
Hey, hold on!

135
00:08:33,080 --> 00:08:33,919
I'm going to kill him.

136
00:08:33,919 --> 00:08:34,900
Why are you stopping me?

137
00:08:34,900 --> 00:08:38,289
A brutal animal like him surely deserves
to be chopped into pieces.

138
00:08:38,289 --> 00:08:40,020
But if you kill him now, at most,

139
00:08:40,130 --> 00:08:41,460
you can vent your anger.

140
00:08:42,190 --> 00:08:44,190
In turn, this might alert the enemy.

141
00:08:44,580 --> 00:08:45,680
What do you mean?

142
00:08:47,690 --> 00:08:50,750
Killing Liu Yuan won't
bring Shen Nian'an back to life.

143
00:08:51,360 --> 00:08:52,760
Only by keeping him alive

144
00:08:53,120 --> 00:08:55,960
will we have a chance
to find the hidden mastermind.

145
00:08:55,960 --> 00:08:56,620
And that...

146
00:08:57,040 --> 00:08:59,420
is the real beginning of your revenge.

147
00:09:00,800 --> 00:09:03,930
Don't you long to avenge Shen Nian'an,
your beloved man?

148
00:09:04,200 --> 00:09:06,000
If you want to find out the truth,

149
00:09:06,840 --> 00:09:07,970
then take my advice.

150
00:09:09,080 --> 00:09:10,680
Do you know who the killer is?

151
00:09:22,640 --> 00:09:23,360
Uncle,

152
00:09:23,360 --> 00:09:25,040
you asked me to come this late at night...

153
00:09:25,040 --> 00:09:25,840
Ah!

154
00:09:26,570 --> 00:09:28,760
Isn't that Prefect Wang?

155
00:09:37,640 --> 00:09:39,240
Look at what you've done!

156
00:09:39,360 --> 00:09:41,120
Why is your name on the list?

157
00:09:48,520 --> 00:09:48,960
It...

158
00:09:49,100 --> 00:09:49,540
It...

159
00:09:49,830 --> 00:09:51,690
How did he find out all about this?

160
00:09:51,740 --> 00:09:53,270
How did he find it out?

161
00:09:54,220 --> 00:09:55,820
Are you seriously asking me?

162
00:09:55,920 --> 00:09:57,850
Shouldn't you be asking yourself?

163
00:09:57,880 --> 00:09:59,880
If he hadn't come meet me first,

164
00:10:00,280 --> 00:10:01,400
you would be brought

165
00:10:01,400 --> 00:10:04,600
to the Minister
of the Court of Judicial Review tomorrow!

166
00:10:04,960 --> 00:10:05,520
Uncle,

167
00:10:05,640 --> 00:10:06,840
p-please forgive me!

168
00:10:06,840 --> 00:10:07,360
It...

169
00:10:07,880 --> 00:10:08,880
It was a momentary

170
00:10:09,000 --> 00:10:10,000
lapse on my part.

171
00:10:11,560 --> 00:10:13,930
You are so careless in your work.

172
00:10:14,080 --> 00:10:17,210
How can I entrust you
with important tasks in the future?

173
00:10:18,270 --> 00:10:20,490
You reproach is justified, Uncle.

174
00:10:20,920 --> 00:10:21,650
I promise...

175
00:10:21,800 --> 00:10:23,680
to act with great caution in the future.

176
00:10:23,680 --> 00:10:24,280
I promise!

177
00:10:25,680 --> 00:10:27,920
What happened to your head?

178
00:10:28,080 --> 00:10:28,680
I...

179
00:10:30,600 --> 00:10:31,880
N-Nothing happened.

180
00:10:32,480 --> 00:10:33,640
I just got hurt

181
00:10:33,640 --> 00:10:35,560
b-by accident.

182
00:10:40,540 --> 00:10:43,740
Jingjing has always had a bad temper
since she was little.

183
00:10:44,360 --> 00:10:45,360
Some things

184
00:10:46,480 --> 00:10:48,400
had better not be rushed.

185
00:10:49,720 --> 00:10:50,680
I understand.

186
00:10:51,460 --> 00:10:53,780
I will follow your instructions, Uncle.

187
00:10:55,610 --> 00:10:57,030
Get rid of the body.

188
00:10:59,480 --> 00:11:00,120
Yes.

189
00:11:00,200 --> 00:11:01,920
Consider it done, Uncle!

190
00:11:13,160 --> 00:11:13,960
Master,

191
00:11:14,480 --> 00:11:16,280
Prime Minister Lin killed Prefect Wang

192
00:11:16,280 --> 00:11:17,480
to cover for Liu Yuan.

193
00:11:17,560 --> 00:11:19,790
Prime Minister Lin is ruthless
and decisive.

194
00:11:19,790 --> 00:11:21,360
There's nothing good in him.

195
00:11:21,360 --> 00:11:22,890
Master, are you suggesting

196
00:11:23,230 --> 00:11:26,520
that Prime Minister Lin
has a lot to do with Lingya Tower?

197
00:11:26,800 --> 00:11:28,260
How are things on your end?

198
00:11:29,170 --> 00:11:31,040
I've reached a consensus
with Lin Jingjing.

199
00:11:31,040 --> 00:11:32,740
Let's just wait and see what happens.

200
00:11:32,740 --> 00:11:33,520
Good.

201
00:11:41,970 --> 00:11:42,770
Yang.

202
00:11:45,650 --> 00:11:46,450
Mr. Liu.

203
00:11:48,440 --> 00:11:49,680
Level with me.

204
00:11:50,480 --> 00:11:52,560
After I brought Miss Lin back to her room,

205
00:11:52,560 --> 00:11:54,240
who else saw us?

206
00:11:55,080 --> 00:11:56,120
No one.

207
00:11:56,160 --> 00:11:57,760
Last night, she came out soon

208
00:11:57,760 --> 00:11:59,190
after entering her room.

209
00:11:59,320 --> 00:12:01,120
No one went in there afterwards.

210
00:12:03,000 --> 00:12:04,440
No one at all?

211
00:12:06,710 --> 00:12:08,570
Could I have been hurt by Miss Lin?

212
00:12:10,160 --> 00:12:10,960
Ah...

213
00:12:14,320 --> 00:12:15,640
Or did you attack me?

214
00:12:15,760 --> 00:12:16,640
No, I didn't.

215
00:12:16,760 --> 00:12:18,560
I was in my room the entire night.

216
00:12:18,560 --> 00:12:20,290
I didn't dare to take a step out.

217
00:12:23,280 --> 00:12:25,400
Keep a close eye on Miss Lin.

218
00:12:25,790 --> 00:12:27,630
Should anything happen,

219
00:12:27,760 --> 00:12:29,400
let me know at once.

220
00:12:29,880 --> 00:12:30,680
Otherwise—

221
00:12:31,480 --> 00:12:32,480
you know

222
00:12:32,530 --> 00:12:34,090
how Shen Nian'an ended up.

223
00:12:34,550 --> 00:12:35,830
Yes, Mr. Liu.

224
00:12:45,480 --> 00:12:46,280
Yang.

225
00:12:47,700 --> 00:12:50,360
I can't believe you're spying on me
for Liu Yuan.

226
00:12:52,920 --> 00:12:54,240
No, I'm not, My Lady.

227
00:13:01,280 --> 00:13:03,440
I heard each and every word

228
00:13:03,440 --> 00:13:05,520
you and Liu Yuan said just now.

229
00:13:05,540 --> 00:13:07,380
No need to deny it.

230
00:13:08,480 --> 00:13:09,320
Who are you?

231
00:13:09,840 --> 00:13:11,600
I don't know what you're talking about.

232
00:13:11,600 --> 00:13:13,280
You agreed to spy on Miss Lin

233
00:13:13,280 --> 00:13:15,240
for Liu Yuan,

234
00:13:15,240 --> 00:13:16,940
so as not to be killed.

235
00:13:17,200 --> 00:13:18,600
I heard that right, didn't I?

236
00:13:18,600 --> 00:13:21,920
He also mentioned about
how Shen Nian'an ended up...

237
00:13:22,000 --> 00:13:23,800
You've worked for me for a long time.

238
00:13:23,800 --> 00:13:26,130
How exactly did you connect with Liu Yuan?

239
00:13:28,200 --> 00:13:29,200
My Lady,

240
00:13:29,400 --> 00:13:30,560
I don't want to die.

241
00:13:30,600 --> 00:13:32,160
I was coerced into Liu's evil plan!

242
00:13:32,160 --> 00:13:33,480
Coerced?

243
00:13:34,000 --> 00:13:36,000
Don't you fear that I might kill you too?

244
00:13:36,000 --> 00:13:36,600
Confess.

245
00:13:36,760 --> 00:13:38,040
What exactly does Liu Yuan have to do

246
00:13:38,040 --> 00:13:39,500
with the death of Nian'an?

247
00:13:40,280 --> 00:13:41,400
My Lady...

248
00:13:43,320 --> 00:13:44,960
If you tell the truth now,

249
00:13:45,080 --> 00:13:46,480
we'll let you live.

250
00:13:48,560 --> 00:13:50,520
But if you dare to lie again,

251
00:13:50,600 --> 00:13:52,280
I'll end your life

252
00:13:52,280 --> 00:13:53,480
on Miss Lin's behalf.

253
00:13:53,800 --> 00:13:54,560
My Lady.

254
00:13:54,560 --> 00:13:56,000
My Lady, I'm sorry I did wrong.

255
00:13:56,000 --> 00:13:57,170
As long as you spare my life,

256
00:13:57,170 --> 00:13:59,000
I'll tell you everything I know, My Lady.

257
00:13:59,000 --> 00:14:00,400
My Lady!

258
00:14:05,080 --> 00:14:06,880
You're so talented with your hands,
My Lady.

259
00:14:06,830 --> 00:14:09,120
[Wish you good health, Nian'an]

260
00:14:07,280 --> 00:14:09,420
But judging from the characters,
this sachet

261
00:14:09,420 --> 00:14:10,770
isn't for Prime Minister Lin, is it?

262
00:14:10,770 --> 00:14:12,230
It's not, you clever girl.

263
00:14:16,480 --> 00:14:18,960
Deliver this to Nian'an's residence today.

264
00:14:18,980 --> 00:14:19,460
Got it.

265
00:14:20,070 --> 00:14:20,670
Wait!

266
00:14:22,240 --> 00:14:23,110
I remember.

267
00:14:23,130 --> 00:14:24,880
I must hand it to him personally.

268
00:14:24,880 --> 00:14:25,640
Understood!

269
00:14:27,810 --> 00:14:30,490
On my way to Mr. Shen's abode that day,

270
00:14:31,320 --> 00:14:32,680
I happened to see him.

271
00:14:33,080 --> 00:14:34,800
So I wanted to greet him.

272
00:14:34,800 --> 00:14:35,400
Mister...

273
00:14:35,490 --> 00:14:39,160
But then I saw him discreetly entering
a tea house through its rear door.

274
00:14:39,160 --> 00:14:40,290
Shortly after that,

275
00:14:40,440 --> 00:14:43,000
I noticed another man
went into the tea house too.

276
00:14:43,000 --> 00:14:44,400
That was exactly Mr. Liu.

277
00:14:44,640 --> 00:14:46,520
It seemed unusual to me,

278
00:14:48,020 --> 00:14:50,620
so I decided to go up to Mr. Shen

279
00:14:50,720 --> 00:14:52,360
after they both came out.

280
00:14:52,890 --> 00:14:53,960
A moment later,

281
00:14:54,440 --> 00:14:56,400
I saw Mr. Shen being carried out.

282
00:14:57,310 --> 00:14:58,670
I was too terrified

283
00:14:58,690 --> 00:14:59,810
to make a sound.

284
00:15:00,490 --> 00:15:01,800
At the very end,

285
00:15:02,200 --> 00:15:04,670
two more people came out of the tea house.

286
00:15:04,780 --> 00:15:05,880
Rest assured, Prime Minister Lin.

287
00:15:05,880 --> 00:15:07,540
I'll be on the task right away.

288
00:15:20,880 --> 00:15:23,000
I-I didn't see anything.

289
00:15:23,700 --> 00:15:24,660
Yang.

